{"word":"H7650 - שָׁבַע - shâbaʻ - shaw-bah' - Adjure","slug":"H7650","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">שָׁבַע</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>shâbaʻ"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>shaw-bah'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Adjure"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05D1;&#x05E2; - sha&#x0302;ba&#x201B;</b> - <i>shaw-bah'</i><p/>A primitive root; properly to <i>be complete</i>, but used only as a denominative from <a href=\"#/H7651\">H7651</a>; to <i>seven</i> oneself, that is, <i>swear</i> (as if by repeating a declaration seven times): - adjure, charge (by an oath, with an oath), feed to the full [by mistake for <a href=\"#/H7646\">H7646</a>], take an oath, X straitly, (cause to, make to) swear."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H7620\">H7620</a>, <a href=\"#/H7621\">H7621</a>, <a href=\"#/H7637\">H7637</a>, <a href=\"#/H7651\">H7651</a>, <a href=\"#/H7652\">H7652</a>, <a href=\"#/H7656\">H7656</a>, <a href=\"#/H7657\">H7657</a>, <a href=\"#/H7658\">H7658</a>, <a href=\"#/H7659\">H7659</a>"}]}